Detailed Description

Exception for Ionic server errors.

Instance Variables:
httpcode (int): The HTTP response code.
servercode (int): The internal server error code. Zero if none was provided by the server.
servermessage (string): The internal server error message. Empty if none was provided by the server.
serverdatajson (string): The internal server error data JSON. Empty if none was provided by the server.
conversationid (string): The conversation ID generated by the client for use in the server request.
